data.text:
Zhirayr Margaryan is an Armenian professional footballer who plays for Urartu.

Zhirayr Margaryan was born on September 13, 1997, in Yerevan, Yerevan, Armenia. His birth geographical coordinates are 40° 10’ 52” North latitude and 44° 30’ 49” East longitude. Zhirayr Margaryan is currently 26 years old.

Astrologically, Zhirayr Margaryan falls under the Sun sign of Virgo, with Scorpio as his Ascendant, Aquarius as his Moon sign, and Virgo as his Black Moon Lilith sign.
